{"tid":61051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"貧困率激增 雅典設淋浴巴士　免費服務露宿者","createTime":"2016-12-31T02:08:08.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-31T10:34:51.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"db58b46b45c9f334b6a4b22f71a16635d9392937","tid":61051,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T02:08:08.000Z","msg":"歐盟統計數字顯示，希臘自2009年底的債務危機開始以來，貧困率激增，近36％的人生活受財困。幾乎四分之一的希臘人失業，不少人流落街頭。在首都雅典廣場，上月就出現一輛改裝巴士，專為露宿者而設，提供淋浴間。 <br />\n<br />\n計劃在11月下旬開始，將會於市內約12個地點停放。是次計劃由希臘慈善機構私人資助。露宿者可免費享受熱水浴，義工亦會發放乾淨內衣和浴室用品。負責人表示，由於「浴室巴士」需要電力、用水和污水排放口，選址有困難，但認為還有更多地方需要這種設施。其中一名露宿者用畢表示感謝，稱：「這好很多了！謝謝。我感謝他們這樣做。」 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20161231/photo/bknint-20161231054318916-1231_17011_001_02b.jpg?20161231062146\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161231%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20161231054318916-1231_17011_001_02b.jpg%3F20161231062146&h=397963cc&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n巴士停放在首都雅典廣場。（互聯網圖片） <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20161231/photo/bknint-20161231054318916-1231_17011_001_03b.jpg?20161231062146\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161231%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20161231054318916-1231_17011_001_03b.jpg%3F20161231062146&h=b85c06eb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n巴士車身漆上水滴圖案。（互聯網圖片） <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20161231/photo/bknint-20161231054318916-1231_17011_001_04b.jpg?20161231062146\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161231%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20161231054318916-1231_17011_001_04b.jpg%3F20161231062146&h=8944319c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n露宿者可以取得乾淨內衣和浴室用品。（互聯網圖片）"},{"pid":"0f23ae2ceb6cdebc78334f08d01dfdb92df7bea6","tid":61051,"uid":2643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T02:09:11.000Z","msg":"叫雞野戰完又可以沖涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平靚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a89235e8c38862d6bdec89a9d5866617bb625b7d","tid":61051,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T07:13:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1403230ef8d8c2a68472bb1f273944c631d3ec25","tid":61051,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T07:16:00.000Z","msg":"個邊女女幾錢q?<br />\n中出+幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc30f4da70bcfe66aff2628f5132c2d77988ff62","tid":61051,"uid":67302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T07:17:45.000Z","msg":"有無連登仔去贈興"},{"pid":"def4bdc3ebf68c17210f65294a39f78278dc229e","tid":61051,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T10:34:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}